com.zendesk.sdk.model

Class CommentResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.zendesk.sdk.model.CommentResponse

  • public class CommentResponse
extends Object
    This is a model class for a CommentResponse object that will be fetched by the ZendeskRequestProvider as part of CommentsResponse.

    This class is a model that will be serialised to JSON and deserialised from JSON to this model. As such it does not follow the m naming prefix for fields.
